Pericles: Mailchimp Newsletter generator from Google Calendar
==============================================================

Pericles takes the all the events for the week and generates a mailchimp
newsletter for them.

Dependencies

 * mailsnake
 * gdata

Running pip install -r requirements.txt ought to work. I'll work on making
a setup.py script later.

Usage:

 * `mv example-sensitive.py sensitive.py` (do not recommit this to github)
 * Change the variables in sensitive.py to your liking
 * Append sensitive.py to your `settings.py`
 * Run `python pericles.py blurb.txt` edit the blurb each week to your liking
